{"tid":1224370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警想洗底","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T03:17:43.000Z","uid":185730,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24ab5049d997ef5569d78c9c5bcb7674c5a932c2","tid":1224370,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】路透社引述資深警務人員︰警隊內不滿特首處理危機「瘋狂」　感成磨心 (10:54)<br />\n<br />\n2019/6/15<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;共1幅&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n下一頁&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威周三（12日）釀成嚴重衝突，多人受傷，警方被批評使用過度武力，引起爭議。路透社周五（14日）引述多名資深警員稱，在今次暴力衝突中感到左右為難。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述「一名在指揮位置的資深警務人員」（a senior law enforcement officer in a command position）說，基於港人長久以來對內地法律制度的不信任，示威者反對修例並非不合理。他表示，警隊內「很多人」（a significant number）感到成為磨心，將這歸咎特首林鄭月娥處理今次危機的手法，形容是「瘋狂」的（&quot;It's madness.&quot;）。他又說，要解決事件，警員及示威者都無能為力，只有林鄭月娥才能解決此事。<br />\n另一名資深執法人員稱，示威者今次更加堅決，如果政府不退讓，暴力勢必會升級。<br />\n<br />\n("},{"pid":"be9a190e1cbbd525fc459934557daa38af33b00e","tid":1224370,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/467336684040660/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F467336684040660%2F&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=342d10b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/467336684040660/</a>"},{"pid":"34aa26d6b901cd8f02898ea3bae7923f4b38ceeb","tid":1224370,"uid":19982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801db00121c4c7cca0721b55a3f24d79dd59c0a3","tid":1224370,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:17:43.000Z","msg":"撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face